        "username": "Brandon_R",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/brandon_r/{size}/2555_2.png",
        "created_at": "2017-07-07T15:31:42.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Scott Everson\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n Scott Everson:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Someone here should pick up one of the 1990 or 1991 Woodward Canyon Chardonnays on WineBid and report back on this thread.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I haven\u2019t looked at these specific ones, but if they\u2019re the regular Columbia Valley bottles, I would be cautious.  If they\u2019re Ceilio Vineyard, I\u2019d go for it.</p>",
